name: Walkie-Talkie-Offline-Online-Ui
description:
Do you want to communicate with your friends and family by means of your phone? Do you want to connect and communicate with your friends or family in the easiest and fastest way possible? Walkie Talkie is the app made just for this purpose. By using walkie talkie, you can easily communicate with your friends or family no matter where you are easily and in the fastest way possible.

Walkie Talkie allows you to establish a connection with your friends or family by means of a wifi connection or Bluetooth connection. After the connection is made between both the devices, you can easily talk with your friends and family using this walkie talkie app.


Download Now->

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.walkietalkie.talkiewalkieoffline.oronlineapp
